> these properties can be removed since Pig projection will read only the required fields.

Could you clarify? Pig signals LoadFunc impls to optimize their
behavior based on required projection. These properties support
implementation of that optimization in SequenceFileLoader. If I remove
them, unnecessary Writable deserialization will take place during
projection.

